&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum 2 years of experience in sales and B2B &lt;/strong&gt;client management (new business development, client retention, and account management)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commercial acumen and proven &lt;strong&gt;negotiation skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent listening and communication abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Highly results-oriented&lt;/strong&gt;, determined, and team-driven&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong &lt;strong&gt;passion for sales&lt;/strong&gt; and a proactive approach to feedback and continuous improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in multicultural, structured, and dynamic environments&lt;/li&gt;

